<template>
    <v-network-graph
      :node-list="nodeList"
      :edge-list="edgeList"
      :node-label="getNodeLabel"
      :edge-label="getEdgeLabel"
    />
  </template>
  
  <script>
  import { VNetworkGraph } from 'v-network-graph';
  
  export default {
    components: {
      VNetworkGraph
    },
    props: {
      nodeList: {
        type: Object,
        required: true
      },
      edgeList: {
        type: Object,
        required: true
      }
    },
    methods: {
      getNodeLabel(node) {
        // Replace this with whatever logic you want to use to display node labels
        return node.name;
      },
      getEdgeLabel(edge) {
        // Replace this with whatever logic you want to use to display edge labels
        return `${edge.source} -> ${edge.target}`;
      }
    }
  }
  </script>
